These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, architect, nurse
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, purple, red
3 different games are played: monopoly, poker, billiard
3 different pets are kept: turtle, bird, mouse
1. the person who likes purple is the architect##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
3. the nurse is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the person playing monopoly is the person who likes red##1
5. the person who likes aquamarine is in the middle##1
6. the nurse is the person who likes red##1
7. the person playing billiard is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |
| Job      | nurse  | musician       | architect   |
| Color          | red | aquamarine | purple |
| Game         | monopoly  | billiard | poker    |
| Pet   | mouse | turtle       | bird      |

