.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, train, skateboard
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, aquamarine, ebony
The people have 3 different jobs:  entrepreneur, lawyer, journalist
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, aconite, amaryllis
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the train##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the lawyer##1
4. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1
6. the person who growsamaryllis is the entrepreneur##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Transport          | snowmobile      | train  | skateboard        |
| Color         | ebony | aquamarine | lavender |
| Job   | entrepreneur | lawyer | journalist       |
| Flower           | amaryllis     | aconite     | begonia      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, swisher, oliveros
House: cottage, wooden, colonial
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, soccer, surfing
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, turquise, brown
1. the colonial house is the person who likes white##1
2. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the wooden house is on the left of the person who likes white##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is in the middle##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the colonial house##1
6. the oliveros-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| Cigar      | swisher    | ritmeester        | oliveros |
| House           | wooden    | colonial | cottage    |
| Sport   | cricket | surfing             | soccer  |
| Color     | brown     | white                | turquise  |

