.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-4::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, lizard
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, volleyball, badminton
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice, hot-chocolate
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, indonesian, american
1. the american is on the right of the indonesian##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the egyptian is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
4. the owner of the cat is the american##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Pet          | goldfish    | lizard  | cat      |
| Sport           | badminton    | rowing | volleyball |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate   | juice  | almond-milk     |
| Nationality   | egyptian | indonesian    | american      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different games are played: monopoly, snooker, bridge
City: prague, boston, berlin
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, february, january
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, tea, soy-milk
1. the person who's birthday is in august is the person traveling to boston##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is the person playing bridge##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is the person playing monopoly##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is the person traveling to prague##1
7. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Game         | bridge | monopoly     | snooker   |
| City           | berlin       | boston   | prague     |
| Birthday   | february     | august | january |
| Beverage           | soy-milk      | mirinda         | tea  |

