.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-6::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, light-blue, mauve
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, iced-tea
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, action, drama
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, prince, bongani
1. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
5. the person watching action movies is on the left of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Color          | ivory | light-blue       | mauve |
| Beverage   | iced-tea     | milk       | mirinda   |
| Movie-Genre           | action      | comedy       | drama     |
| Cigar         | bolivar   | prince | bongani  |

