.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-7::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, snowmobile, motorbike
City: marseilles, venice, rome
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, milk, juice
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, poker
1. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person playing poker is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2        |     3      |
| Transport          | motorbike       | snowmobile         | skateboard   |
| City           | marseilles | rome | venice |
| Beverage   | coffee     | milk        | juice        |
| Game   | bridge      | mah-jongg           | poker        |

