.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-8::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, plum, potato
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, iced-tea, coffee
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, blue, black
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, writer, security-guard
1. the coach is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes black is the security-guard##1
3. the person eating potato is in the middle##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
5. the person who likes black is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the coach is the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Food         | plum   | potato | carrot |
| Beverage   | tea | coffee         | iced-tea       |
| Color           | ebony      | black      | blue         |
| Job     | writer      | security-guard         | coach          |

