.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-9::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, banana, radish
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, apricot, aquamarine
3 different games are played: billiard, scrabble, go
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, cycling, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is in the middle##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
3. the person eating banana is the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person who likes brown is the person playing go##1
5. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left##1
6. the person eating radish is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| Food       | banana            | raspberry      | radish  |
| Color         | aquamarine | brown | apricot |
| Game         | billiard               | go | scrabble |
| Sport   | cycling             | sailing       | water-polo      |

