.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-10::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, february, november
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, woodworking, board-games
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, iris, balloon-flower
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, sailing
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
6. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Birthday           | november | september         | february |
| Hobby   | collecting      | woodworking | board-games     |
| Flower   | marigold   | iris       | balloon-flower     |
| Sport           | sailing    | basketball         | badminton        |

