.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-11::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, collecting, fishing
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, water, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, basketball, weightlifting
City: marseilles, nizza, london
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
6. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |
| Hobby           | collecting | fishing | filmmaking |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate        | water       | milk     |
| Sport   | basketball     | weightlifting         | soccer     |
| City     | london | nizza          | marseilles      |

