.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-12::.
There 3 different types of food: grapes, grapefruit, garlic
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, camping, card-games
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, doctor, dancer
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, april, october
1. the person who's birthday is in october is the doctor##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
3. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |      3      |
| Food      | garlic    | grapefruit | grapes |
| Hobby   | camping | hiking     | card-games     |
| Job   | dancer        | doctor        | mechanic        |
| Birthday           | april    | october         | june     |

