.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-13::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, iced-tea
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, mystery, documentary
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, oliveros, aristoff
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, apricot, azure
1. the person who likes azure is the person drinking coffee##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person who likes azure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3     |
| Beverage         | almond-milk | coffee | iced-tea   |
| Movie-Genre           | documentary     | martial-arts    | mystery   |
| Cigar   | oliveros         | aristoff    | baccarat   |
| Color         | apricot       | azure | lilac |

