.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-14::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, december, march
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, photographer, engineer
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, pall-mall, siglo
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, classical, folk
1. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is the bongani-smoker##1
3. the engineer is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the photographer##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is the fan of folk##1
6. the fan of classical is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |
| Birthday    | january | december     | march      |
| Job        | architect | photographer       | engineer |
| Cigar       | pall-mall | bongani | siglo  |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | jazz   | folk  |

