.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-15::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, skiing, climbing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, romance, zombie
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, brazilian, french
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, blend, bluemaster
1. the siglo-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the french##1
3. the blend-smoker is the australian##1
4. the australian is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is in the middle##1
6. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3      |
| Sport      | climbing | sailing | skiing       |
| Movie-Genre          | zombie     | adventure   | romance       |
| Nationality         | australian  | french   | brazilian |
| Cigar   | blend   | bluemaster       | siglo  |

