.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-17::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, bolivar, aristoff
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, lily, iris
City: marseilles, san-francisco, edinburgh
3 different games are played: canasta, whist, go
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person playing go##1
4. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
6. the person who growsiris is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |    3    |
| Cigar      | aristoff      | bolivar    | vegafina    |
| Flower          | iris         | lily    | bellflower   |
| City           | marseilles | edinburgh | san-francisco |
| Game   | go         | canasta     | whist    |

