House: tower, cottage, futuristic
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the tower house is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
5. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |
| Sport      | snowboarding  | baseball   | surfing  |
| Hobby          | chess   | cooking | traveling   |
| Birthday   | september      | august      | june    |
| House   | cottage | tower    | futuristic |

