.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-19::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, balloon-flower, dahlia
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, eggplant, dahliacher
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, february, september
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, blood-red, ivory
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who likes red##1
2. the person eating dahliacher is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is the person who likes red##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
5. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person who likes red##1
6. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Flower      | balloon-flower         | dahlia     | amaryllis     |
| Food           | eggplant        | dahliacher | blueberry |
| Birthday   | february        | september   | june    |
| Color         | ivory | red   | blood-red |

