.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
3 different games are played: domino, scrabble, whist
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, daisy, amaryllis
City: prague, miami, venice
There are 3 different nationalities: french, brazilian, japanese
1. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person playing domino##1
3. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the brazilian##1
4. the french is on the far left##1
5. the brazilian is in the middle##1
6. the person who growslily is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| Game          | whist     | scrabble    | domino    |
| Flower         | lily | amaryllis | daisy     |
| City   | prague  | miami      | venice        |
| Nationality         | french   | brazilian   | japanese |

 